author: Doina Chiacu
title: Stuck at home and jobless, Americans confront growing costs of coronavirus
description: A record 6.6 million Americans filed for unemployment benefits last week, the U.S. government said on Thursday, after another four states told residents to stay at home in the latest signs of the human and economic cost of the coronavirus.
